100+ Python Exercises

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Level Criteria
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Level 1:	Beginner
    Completed an introductory Python course
    Capable of solving simple problems with 1 or 2 Python classes or functions
    Solutions are easily found online or in programming textbooks
    
Level 2:	Intermediate 
    Completed an introductory Python course but possesses a strong programming background from previous languages
    Capable of solving advanced toy problems with 3 or more Python classes or functions
    Solutions are difficult to find online or in programming textbooks
    
Level 3:	Advanced
    In-depth knowledge of Python 
    Capable of solving complex real world problems using more libraries, functions, data structures and algorithms
    Solutions utilize several Python standard packages and advanced techniques and are relevant to current industry challenges

